2026-04-16 21:30:34 - llm.aliyun_llm - INFO - 收到 LLM API 响应  result={'choices': [{'message': {'content': 'Now I have the product spec content. Let me also read the requirements document to compare, then write the review report.', 'reasoning_content': "I've read the product spec document. Now I need to:\n1. Verify the product spec against the requirements document\n2. Write a review/验收 report to /workspace/review_result.md\n3. Notify Human about the checkpoint (optional per SOP)\n4. Mark the task_done message as processed\n\nLet me first read the requirements document to compare, then write the review report.\n\nActually, I already have the requirements document content from earlier sessions. Let me recall it:\n\nThe requirements document had:\n- 项目背景: 宠物健康记录App\n- 目标: 解决宠物主人管理多只宠物健康信息分散、易遗忘的问题\n- 边界范围内: 多宠物档案管理、宠物基本信息记录、疫苗接种记录与提醒、健康事件记录、疫苗到期推送提醒\n- 边界范围外: 宠物社区/社交功能（待澄清）、在线问诊或预约兽医功能（待澄清）、宠物电商/用品购买功能（明确不做）\n- 约束: 目标平台（待澄清）、上线时间（待澄清）、技术栈（待澄清）、数据存储隐私合规\n- 风险: 疫苗提醒依赖通知权限、多宠物数据量性能、疫苗数据来源（待澄清）\n- 待澄清5个问题\n\nNow let me verify the product spec against these requirements:\n\n1. 产品概述清晰 - ✅ The product overview clearly describes the purpose\n2. 用户故事完整 - ✅ Three user stories covering multi-pet management, vaccine reminders, and health event recording\n3. 功能规格可执行 - ✅ Detailed feature table with priorities and acceptance criteria\n4. 验收标准可测试 - ✅ Each user story has specific acceptance criteria with Given/When/Then format\n\nLet me check more carefully:\n- 多宠物档案管理 → covered in Story 1 and feature table ✅\n- 疫苗接种记录与提醒 → covered in Story 2 and feature table ✅\n- 健康事件记录 → covered in Story 3 and feature table ✅\n- 疫苗到期推送提醒 → covered in Story 2 ✅\n- 范围外功能明确列出 ✅\n- 待澄清事项保留 ✅\n- 风险考虑（通知权限拒绝）→ covered in Story 2 boundary case ✅\n\nThe product spec looks comprehensive and well-structured. I'll write a passing review report.\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Write the review report to /workspace/review_result.md using write-output skill\n2. Notify Human about the checkpoint\n3. Mark the task_done message as processed\n\nLet me proceed step by step.", 'role': 'assistant', 'tool_calls': [{'function': {'arguments': '{"skill_name": "write-output", "task_context": "读取需求文档 /mnt/shared/needs/requirements.md 的内容，用于对照验收产品文档。需要使用sandbox_file_operations的read操作读取文件内容。"}', 'name': 'skill_loader'}, 'id': 'tool-152e406b1cc34718bbf843f0a42879ee', 'index': 0, 'type': 'function'}]}, 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'index': 0, 'logprobs': None}], 'object': 'chat.completion', 'usage': {'prompt_tokens': 12731, 'completion_tokens': 624, 'total_tokens': 13355, 'completion_tokens_details': {'reasoning_tokens': 548}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 7871}}, 'created': 1776346235, 'system_fingerprint': None, 'model': 'glm-5.1', 'id': 'chatcmpl-2473535f-a22a-99f2-bedf-980d7a09813e'}
