2026-04-16 21:31:20 - llm.aliyun_llm - INFO - 收到 LLM API 响应  result={'choices': [{'message': {'content': 'Now I have both documents. Let me create the verification report and write it to the output file.', 'reasoning_content': 'Now I have both the product spec and the requirements document. Let me compare them and create a verification report.\n\nLet me analyze the product spec against the requirements:\n\n**Requirements coverage check:**\n\n1. **多宠物档案管理（添加、编辑、删除宠物信息）** → Covered in Story 1 and Function Spec (P0 宠物档案管理) ✅\n2. **宠物基本信息记录（名称、品种、年龄、体重等）** → Covered in Story 1 (名称、品种、年龄、体重、性别、照片) ✅\n3. **疫苗接种记录与提醒** → Covered in Story 2 and Function Spec (P0 疫苗记录管理, P0 疫苗到期提醒) ✅\n4. **健康事件记录（就医、用药、手术等）** → Covered in Story 3 and Function Spec (P0 健康事件记录) ✅\n5. **疫苗到期推送提醒** → Covered in Story 2 (推送提醒, 未授权时红色标记) ✅\n\n**Verification criteria:**\n\n1. **产品概述清晰** → ✅ Section 1 provides clear product overview\n2. **用户故事完整** → ✅ Three user stories with acceptance criteria and edge cases\n3. **功能规格可执行** → ✅ Function spec table with priority, description, and acceptance criteria\n4. **验收标准可测试** → ✅ Each user story has testable acceptance criteria with Given-When-Then format\n\n**Additional positives:**\n- Target users table is well-defined\n- Out of scope section prevents scope creep\n- Pending clarification items tracked with assumptions\n- Edge cases considered (notification permission denied, data validation)\n\n**Minor issues:**\n- The product spec still has "待澄清事项" that haven\'t been resolved by Human - but this is expected since Human confirmed the requirements with these items still pending, and PM made reasonable assumptions\n- Data privacy compliance (mentioned in requirements constraints) is not explicitly addressed in the product spec - this could be a minor gap\n\nOverall, the product spec is well-structured and covers all the required functionality. I\'ll mark it as ✅ 通过 with a note about the privacy compliance gap.\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Write the verification report to /workspace/review_result.md using write-output skill\n2. Notify Human about the checkpoint (optional per SOP)\n3. Mark the task_done message as processed\n\nLet me write the verification report first.', 'role': 'assistant', 'tool_calls': [{'function': {'arguments': '{"skill_name": "write-output", "task_context": "将验收报告写入 /workspace/review_result.md。验收报告内容如下：\\n\\n# 验收报告 - 宠物健康记录App\\n\\n**验收时间**：2026-04-16T13:30:00+00:00\\n**验收人**：Manager\\n**被验收文档**：/mnt/shared/design/product_spec.md\\n\\n## 验收结论\\n\\n**结论**：✅ 通过\\n\\n## 检查项\\n\\n| 检查项 | 是否满足 | 说明 |\\n|--------|---------|------|\\n| 产品概述清晰 | ✅ | 第1节明确描述了产品定位：为宠物主人提供健康记录管理App，解决多宠信息分散和疫苗遗忘问题 |\\n| 用户故事完整 | ✅ | 3个核心用户故事覆盖全部需求功能：多宠物档案管理、疫苗记录与提醒、健康事件记录。每个故事含验收标准和边界情况 |\\n| 功能规格可执行 | ✅ | 功能规格表包含8个功能模块，每个模块有优先级（P0/P1/P2）、功能描述和验收标准，可直接指导开发 |\\n| 验收标准可测试 | ✅ | 用户故事验收标准采用Given-When-Then格式，可转化为测试用例；边界情况已考虑（通知权限拒绝、数据校验） |\\n\\n## 需求覆盖度检查\\n\\n| 需求项 | 是否覆盖 | 对应位置 |\\n|--------|---------|---------|\\n| 多宠物档案管理（添加、编辑、删除） | ✅ | 用户故事一 + 功能规格P0 |\\n| 宠物基本信息记录（名称、品种、年龄、体重等） | ✅ | 用户故事一（含性别、照片） |\\n| 疫苗接种记录与提醒 | ✅ | 用户故事二 + 功能规格P0 |\\n| 健康事件记录（就医、用药、手术等） | ✅ | 用户故事三 + 功能规格P0 |\\n| 疫苗到期推送提醒 | ✅ | 用户故事二（含未授权降级方案：红色标记+引导开启权限） |\\n\\n## 亮点\\n\\n1. **通知权限降级方案**：用户拒绝通知授权时，App内仍显示红色标记并引导开启权限，覆盖了需求中\\"疫苗提醒依赖通知权限\\"的风险\\n2. **目标用户分层**：区分多宠主人、单宠新手、日常主人三类用户，有助于后续功能优先级决策\\n3. **范围外明确**：5项明确不做的功能，防止范围蔓延\\n4. **待澄清事项跟踪**：5个待澄清问题均列出影响和当前假设，便于后续迭代澄清\\n\\n## 建议改进（非返工项，后续迭代可优化）\\n\\n1. **隐私合规**：需求约束中提到\\"数据存储需考虑隐私合规\\"，产品规格中未显式说明数据存储和隐私保护方案，建议后续补充数据安全章节\\n2. **数据导出格式细化**：P2功能\\"数据导出\\"的验收标准较笼统，建议细化导出PDF/图片的具体内容模板\\n\\n## 返工要求\\n\\n无。产品文档质量达标，验收通过。\\n\\n输出文件路径：/workspace/review_result.md"}', 'name': 'skill_loader'}, 'id': 'tool-6052f55cd5204174ba18492741d8f205', 'index': 0, 'type': 'function'}]}, 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'index': 0, 'logprobs': None}], 'object': 'chat.completion', 'usage': {'prompt_tokens': 12816, 'completion_tokens': 1227, 'total_tokens': 14043, 'completion_tokens_details': {'reasoning_tokens': 510}, 'prompt_tokens_details'